    "text": {
      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">People</a> * Jean-Francois Romang</b>\n</p>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:198px;\"><a href=\"/File:JFRomang.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/3/37/JFRomang.jpg\" width=\"196\" height=\"218\" class=\"thumbimage\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/File:JFRomang.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>Jean-Francois Romang <sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></div></div></div> \n<p><b>Jean-François Romang</b>,<br />\na French computer scientist and chess programmer. Along with <a href=\"/index.php?title=Raphael_Grundrich&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Raphael Grundrich (page does not exist)\">Raphael Grundrich</a> and <a href=\"/index.php?title=Thomas_Adolph&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Thomas Adolph (page does not exist)\">Thomas Adolph</a>, Jean-Francois Romang is co-author of the <a href=\"/Chess_Engine_Communication_Protocol\" title=\"Chess Engine Communication Protocol\">Chess Engine Communication Protocol</a> and <a href=\"/UCI\" title=\"UCI\">UCI</a> compatible chess engine <a href=\"/Cassandre\" title=\"Cassandre\">Cassandre</a>, which started as a student project at <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Louis_Pasteur_University\">Louis Pasteur University</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Strasbourg\">Strasbourg</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>. Along with <a href=\"/index.php?title=David_Rabel&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"David Rabel (page does not exist)\">David Rabel</a>, Jean-Francois is co-author the <a href=\"/UCI\" title=\"UCI\">UCI</a> compliant chess engine <a href=\"/Gaia\" title=\"Gaia\">Gaïa</a>, and wrote the <a href=\"/Android\" title=\"Android\">Android</a> <a href=\"/UCI\" title=\"UCI\">UCI</a> compliant <a href=\"/GUI\" title=\"GUI\">GUI</a> <a href=\"/index.php?title=ChessPad&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"ChessPad (page does not exist)\">ChessPad</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup> <sup id=\"cite_ref-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup>. \n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#PicoChess\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">PicoChess</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Forum_Posts\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Forum Posts</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#External_Links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External Links</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"PicoChess\">PicoChess</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Jean-Francois_Romang&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: PicoChess\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<p>Jean-François Romang's project <a href=\"/PicoChess\" title=\"PicoChess\">PicoChess</a> is a <a href=\"/Dedicated_Chess_Computers\" title=\"Dedicated Chess Computers\">dedicated chess computer</a> based on <a href=\"/Stockfish\" title=\"Stockfish\">Stockfish</a> and <a href=\"/DGT_Board\" title=\"DGT Board\">DGT Board</a>, in the meantime supported by <a href=\"/index.php?title=Shivkumar_Shivaji&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Shivkumar Shivaji (page does not exist)\">Shivkumar Shivaji</a> and <a href=\"/index.php?title=J%C3%BCrgen_Pr%C3%A9cour&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Jürgen Précour (page does not exist)\">Jürgen Précour</a>. \n</p>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Forum_Posts\">Forum Posts</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Jean-Francois_Romang&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: Forum Posts\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=334869\">Fast check detection in bitboard engine</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Jean-Francois Romang</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, December 10, 2003</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=39118\">New opensource GUI on android for UCI engines</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Jean-Francois Romang</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, May 19, 2011</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=44901\">Raspberry Pi / Stockfish dedicated chess computer/board</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Jean-Francois Romang</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, August 26, 2012</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=44930\">PicoChess stand alone chess computer has born&#160;:-)</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Jean-Francois Romang</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, August 28, 2012</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=45329\">PicoChess finally on Raspberry Pi</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Jean-Francois Romang</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, September 25, 2012&#160;» <a href=\"/Raspberry_Pi\" title=\"Raspberry Pi\">Raspberry Pi</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=47869\">Unofficial stockfish 28.04.2013 with rtb tablebases support</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Jean-Francois Romang</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, April 28, 2013</li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_Links\">External Links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Jean-Francois_Romang&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: External Links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://cassandre.sourceforge.net/\">Cassandre - Chess Engine</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://gaiachess.free.fr/\">Gaïa Chess Engine</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.picochess.org/\">PicoChess</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Jean-Francois Romang</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://github.com/jromang?tab=repositories\">jromang (Jean-Francois Romang) · GitHub</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Jean-Francois_Romang&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a href=\"/FCCC_2003\" title=\"FCCC 2003\">FCCC 2003</a>, image snipped from a photo by <a href=\"/Sylvain_Renard\" title=\"Sylvain Renard\">Sylvain Renard</a>, hosted by <a href=\"/St%C3%A9phane_Nguyen\" title=\"Stéphane Nguyen\">Stéphane Nguyen</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.ludochess.com/fccc2003/tournoi.php3\">Massy, France - 4 &amp; 5 Oct 2003 - 10ème Championnat Français de Programmes d'Echecs</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-2\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://cassandre.sourceforge.net/\">Cassandre - Chess Engine</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-3\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.assembla.com/code/chesspad/subversion/nodes\">Source | Source/SVN | Assembla - ChessPad</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-4\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-4\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=39118\">New opensource GUI on android for UCI engines</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Jean-Francois Romang</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, May 19, 2011</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div>\n<p><b><a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">Up one level</a></b>\n</p>\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260301031724\nCache expiry: 86400\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.016 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.018 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 75/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 166/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 0/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 0/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 2/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%    0.000      1 -total\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key oscar70_mw1-mw_:pcache:idhash:5718-0!canonical and timestamp 20260301031724 and revision id 19684\n --